data.description: Exceptionally well-maintained all-brick ranch home, lovingly cared for by only one family - a rare find! Inside you'll find beautifully refinished original hardwood floors throughout most of the home and brand new carpet in the living room. The sophisticated kitchen was renovated in 2017 with custom cabinets, granite countertops, stainless appliances and a gas stove. You can put your mind at ease -- the roof, HVAC, water heater, windows and interior & exterior doors were all replaced in 2017, as well as updated electrical and plumbing. Bonus room can be a 4th bedroom with a closet added, office or den. Enjoy the spacious and meticulously landscaped backyard, completely fenced-in for privacy. Fantastic location - only 6 minutes to the Savannah historic district, a 5-minute walk to the Enmarket Arena, and easy access to Hwy 516, I-16 and the Talmadge Bridge.
